These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, artichoke
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | iced-tea |
| Food       | eggplant | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta |
| Sport      | handball     | biathlon  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, indian
1. the dutch is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | mystery  |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian |

 #################################

 
